trans-unit.source: How do I install a Visual Studio for Mac preview build?
trans-unit.target: How do I install a Visual Studio for Mac preview build?

trans-unit.source: The latest Preview build of Visual Studio for Mac can be downloaded and installed via the Preview channel in the IDE’s updater.
trans-unit.target: The latest Preview build of Visual Studio for Mac can be downloaded and installed via the Preview channel in the IDE’s updater.

trans-unit.source: For information on switching to the Preview channel, see the Updating Visual Studio for Mac article.
trans-unit.target: For information on switching to the Preview channel, see the Updating Visual Studio for Mac article.
